data.description: In the heart of Garrett, this home is suited with 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and 1,480 square feet and ready for a new owner! Updated in 2021, there is little left to change with a new roof, siding, and much more. Approaching the home, enjoy the warm welcome the wrapped porch brings, while giving you a space to enjoy your mornings, or winding down in the evening. The main entry brings an open concept, giving you a functional space to work with. Off this space, an archway enters into the secluded living room allowing sound control and a bit of privacy, while still feeling connected to the rest of the main level. A second archway leads you to the beautiful formal dining room, perfect for hosting special events. The kitchen is beautifully updated as well giving you a great amount of space and laundry hookup as well. The white subway tile is a nice touch against the white cabinetry and beige tone counters. A convenient back door is an easy access for those grilling days and cookouts. Just to top off the convenience, a half bath available for your guests and quick trips. Heading upstairs you’ll find two bedrooms, a full bath, and an amazing master bedroom suite. This suite offers a large bedroom with a separate space allowing you a seating area, hobby space, or extra storage room. Not just one walk-in closet, but two! Enjoy all this home has to offer, between the substantial updates, spacious layout, and great location.
